These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Transport: ship, bus, snowmobile
1. Transport:bus is on the right of Transport:snowmobile##1
2. Transport:ship is on the far right##1
3. Transport:ship is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Transport   | snowmobile | bus | ship |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Hobby: magic-tricks, woodworking, rock-climbing
1. Hobby:woodworking is in an odd position##4
2. Hobby:magic-tricks is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | rock-climbing | woodworking |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
House: art-deco, colonial, cottage
1. House:colonial is in an even position##4
2. House:colonial is on the left or right of House:cottage##3
3. House:cottage is on the right of House:colonial##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| House   | art-deco | colonial | cottage |

 #################################
 
